src:
Små rörelser på Wall Street – Tinderägaren tappade
De ledande börserna i New York visade upp små rörelser i onsdagshandeln. USA:s handelsminister Wilbur Ross sade att han är optimistisk om att kunna slutföra ”fas ett”-avtalet med Kina, men det tolkades som i linje med vad som redan har sagts på senare tid.
06 Nov 2019, 21:02 by Nyhetsbyrån Direkt, Di

text:
Small movements on Wall Street - Tinder owner dropped
The leading New York stock exchanges showed small movements in Wednesday's trading. US Secretary of Commerce Wilbur Ross said he was optimistic about being able to finalize the "phase one" agreement with China, but it was interpreted as in line with what has been said recently.
06 Nov 2019, 21:02 by News Agency Direct, Tue.
